race.description: Grow Better Garden Products Maiden Plate
race.comment: CINCINCITY (3) improved last start finding one better over 1209m at Yarra Valley, beaten only 1.3 lengths after being prominent at the corner. Faces an easier assignment and with average luck she will be tough to beat. LICENTIOUS (8) returned from a spell over 1200m at Sandown-Lakeside and was outgraded. She'd jumped out well and won't know herself in this company. Has a 2kg claim and fitter looks well placed to break through. COSTALOTTA (7) needed the first up outing and her synthetic form last preparation reads well enough. Has the inside barrier and quick improvement is likely. SIBUN (9) has the blinkers on for the first time and is a likely improver.
